{
  "texts": [
    "The Department of Mines and Geology of Nepal is currently collating all the information with the intent of producing a detailed geological map at a 1: 50 000 scale.",
    "However, this is a work in progress that still misses most of the study areas considered in this study.",
    "This major limitation affected our ability to consider geology in this article.",
    "Therefore, although we are aware of its relevance in any landslide study, geological information is not explicitly included as a predictor in the modeling protocol presented below.",
    "To partition our study area, we use the same mapping unit defined by Kincey et al. (2021)."
  ]
}